        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Homeland Security Assessment of Terrorists Use of Ghost Guns Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to annually disseminate a terrorism threat assessment regarding ghost guns (i.e., guns without serial numbers) .</p>]]></text>
